  "text": "As we progress into the second 25, 000-year cycle, did— At this time, during this period, was this the period of Lemuria? I am Ra. This is incorrect. However, those who escaped the destruction of Lemuria by natural catastrophe and were thus of Lemurian background continued their learn/teachings at locations ranging from your South America onward through the Americas as you know them and continuing over what was at that time a bridge which no longer exists. There were those in what you would call Russia…",
